# The following lines are desirable for IPv6 capable hosts
::1     ip6-localhost ip6-loopback
fe00::0 ip6-localnet
ff00::0 ip6-mcastprefix
ff02::1 ip6-allnodes
ff02::2 ip6-allrouters


#
# Finnish blocklist extension for a list from
# http://someonewhocares.org/hosts/hosts
# and
# https://github.com/StevenBlack/hosts
#
# My rules for technology usage
#
# 1. It is time for a walk when the sun is shining
# 2. Read books not news, news makes you stupid
# 3. Be social: reading social media is not a social activity
# 4. Mobile phone is a tracking device, avoid it
# 5. Physical labour is better than non-physical labour
# 6. Being in forests is important: experience trees and lakes
#
# You can make your own rules :)
#
# You can easily block harmfull material.
# 0.0.0.0 some_harmful_domain
# For instance,
